      <p>Our comprehensive data table below illustrates the exact cash amounts distributed annually. We have aggregated the regular quarterly payouts, and where applicable, noted any special, one-time dividends that FXAIX may have authorized to distribute excess windfall profits or asset sale proceeds.</p>

